before_layer_change_gcode:
;BEFORE_LAYER_CHANGE
;[layer_num]:: [layer_z]mm

; If the print height is above 150mm, we want to issue a warning
; 20231025 - have to exist here because `max_layer_z` is not supported in Start Gcode
{if layer_num == 0 and max_layer_z > 120}M291 P"Tall print detected and needs additional physical setup. Press CANCEL to quit." R"!! WARNING !!" S3{endif}

; Initial
G92 E0.0
machine_end_gcode:
G4 ; wait

M221 S100 ; reset flow
M572 D0 S0.0 ; reset pressure advance

{if print_settings_id=~/.*(DETAIL @MK3|QUALITY @MK3|@0.25 nozzle MK3).*/}M907 E538 ; reset extruder motor current{endif}

M104 S0 ; turn off temperature
M140 S0 ; turn off heatbed
M107 ; turn off fan
M144 ; Set bed to standby

{if max_layer_z < max_print_height}G1 Z{z_offset+min(max_layer_z+10, max_print_height)}{endif} ; Move print head up
G1 X10 Y210 F1500 ; home X axis
M84 ; disable motors

; Beep twice
M300 S1700 P1000
G4 P2000
M300 S1700 P1000
G4 P2000
machine_start_gcode:
; Initialize
G90 ; use absolute coordinates
M83 ; extruder relative mode

M109 S180                           ; heat up the nozzle first (to warm up the PINDA)
G1 E-0.5 F4800                      ; retract filament quickly

G28 ; Home
M190 S[first_layer_bed_temperature] ; wait for bed temp
M109 S[first_layer_temperature]     ; wait for extruder temp

; Beep
M300 S1200 P1500
G4 P3000

G30 ; Rehome Z
G29 S0 ; mesh bed leveling

G1 X30.0 Y0.0 F2500 ; go outside print area
G1 Z0.2 F720
G92 E0
G1 E12 F300; Blob
G1 X70 E5 F1000; Intro line
G92 E0
name: Prusa MK3S 0.6 nozzle
